512x512
A stylized 2048 game board with a 4x4 grid of tiles, each tile labeled with numbers 2, 4, 8, 16, 32, 64, 128, 256, 512, 1024, 2048. The board is centered on a dark background, with a subtle gradient. The tiles are rounded rectangles with a soft glow, and the highest tile (2048) is highlighted with a golden glow. The overall design is clean and modern, suitable for a web app logo.
